-1433021357.text: "Both IL6 and TGFbeta exposure attenuated luciferase activity of the Ces3-1.4 k reporter with putative signal transducer and activator of transcription 3 (STAT3) - and MAD homolog 3 (SMAD3)-binding sites in Hepa1c1 cells, but they did not affect the Ces3-0.7 k reporter without the sites (XREF_FIG)."
